# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# REDISTRIBUTION-RESTRICTED SOURCE DOCUMENTS — safety net
#
# These live in ../compliance-atlas-reference-private/ (outside this tree) and
# must NEVER be committed: git history is permanent and this repository is
# intended to become public. See reference/SOURCES.md for what each file is and
# where to re-download it.
#
# The patterns below are a backstop against an accidental re-copy into the tree.
# They are name-level, so they do not block the public-domain NIST PDFs.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

# The private sibling directory itself, in case it is ever copied inside.
compliance-atlas-reference-private/
reference-private/

# AICPA Trust Services Criteria (copyright AICPA; download license, no redistribution)
AICPA-TSC-2017-2022POF.pdf
AICPA-TSC-2017-2022POF.txt
**/AICPA-*

# Microsoft SSPA Data Protection Requirements (vendor supplier-program document)
DPR-v12.pdf
DPR-v12.txt
**/DPR-v*

# PCI SSC document-library capture (license-gated; the saved file is an HTML gate page)
pci-dss-401.pdf
**/pci-dss-*.pdf

# Microsoft Learn service-description captures (Microsoft Terms of Use; cite the live URL instead)
purview-service-description.md
**/*-service-description.md

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Scratch
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
scratch/
tmp/
*.tmp
